{"tid":2339186,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"奇文分享：反對全民造星內定造馬，左翼「大獨裁者」列寧有妙計實行過？","createTime":"2020-12-24T12:36:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T08:53:11.000Z","uid":276028,"like":2,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e82faa1405fbe06e6f41aa85b1351c5364bf820d","tid":2339186,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T12:36:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.boyangu.com/art/cultural_studies/kingmakeriii/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.boyangu.com%2Fart%2Fcultural_studies%2Fkingmakeriii%2F&d=z%2FAKp4ZZwI77wMFl%2FSXGt62paxXJRTFpYESBXKIXFX0%3D&h=27a4652a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.boyangu.com/art/cultural_studies/kingmakeriii/</a><br />\n全民造星III疑似造馬內定，是因為甚麼難言之隱？原來左翼的大獨裁者列寧一早有政策應對，可以防止類似全民造星III的造馬，並且嘗試實行過？蘇聯早期的媒體政策十分寬容，連主張復辟專制的內容也能登！？究竟是甚麼政策可以防止全民造星III的造馬？媒體民主化？"},{"pid":"ce6db6b8e9ae7c434297eadde2101f754793e173","tid":2339186,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T13:13:55.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"f348890fafa3ed0f88359c9d208740deede086f3","tid":2339186,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T03:51:10.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"4c123e0db46c498ca75e3dc5dbebf645fe4d494c","tid":2339186,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T08:10:05.000Z","msg":"自推。"},{"pid":"0930a0cc91be966b5391296991121d60c37fdcf1","tid":2339186,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T12:47:51.000Z","msg":"差啲開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60be9d8ee6e47983cc1a07f2df0ab0b95195d81","tid":2339186,"uid":276028,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"0930a0cc91be966b5391296991121d60c37fdcf1","tid":2339186,"uid":228223,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-2